ygData.subject: Confound Those Blasted Lizards!

ygData.messageBody:
Anyone who thinks a train in Blackburrow or
crushbone is hell you havent even felt the horror of
Cazic-Thule. Last night i was killed in 6 trains(only 3 of
them were made by my group....shhhhhh) anyway being in
one of those trains is like havin 4 or 5 ammbasador
D'Vinns after you =) Over all i made about 1 and a half
bubbles of exp. I gave up after most of my group
left.<br>Oh well on a hapier subject i managed to get my
hands on a Staff of Writhing (del 33, dam 9, -9 cha,
and spell effect chaotic feedback wich will do about
50pts of damage as soon as i hit level 30) quite a
quality weapon. I now also have full Bronze armor wich i
think looks prety slick. Hehe i just had to tell my
progress. =)<br><br>Kaylin Danmor, 23rd League Standing,
Minstrel of Norrath
